title: Custom 16 Round Liberator Grip
description:
I made this in a couple days while learning my way around Solidworks.

Print and assemble with regular Liberator parts.

I have designed this to the best of my ability, but do not hold me responsible for anything that this is used for or is the result of.

I have not actually printed this part, but it should work (I measured everything out). Should be strong enough, but I'm not sure, tell me if it isn't.

Best of luck!
